# Long-Term Vision

The future internet will contain billions of autonomous systems participating in economic activity.

Those systems will:

* Purchase services
* Negotiate contracts
* Allocate budgets
* Manage resources
* Coordinate organizations

Economic activity requires identity.

Identity requires trust.

Trust requires infrastructure.

Agent Wallets provide the economic identity layer of the agent internet.

